  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Warehouse Manager Simulator, where you build your logistics empire from the ground up.<br>In Warehouse Manager Simulator, you'll take on the role of a entrepreneur tasked with running and expanding your very own warehouse.<br><br>Run Your Own Warehouse: Purchase, organize, and manage your warehouse space efficiently to maximize profits. From accepting deliveries to fulfilling orders, every aspect of warehouse operations is in your hands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Forklift Fun: Take control of the forklift and maneuver it through the warehouse environment. Upgrade your forklift to handle heavier loads and increase efficiency.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Diverse Pallet Management: Deal with a variety of pallet types, each with its own storage requirements. From regular pallets to refrigerated and hazardous ones, make sure that every item is stored safely and correctly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Expansion: Customize and expand your warehouse to optimize efficiency and maximize profits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to Warehouse Manager Simulator, where you build your logistics empire from the ground up.<br>In Warehouse Manager Simulator, you'll take on the role of a entrepreneur tasked with running and expanding your very own warehouse.<br><br>Run Your Own Warehouse: Purchase, organize, and manage your warehouse space efficiently to maximize profits. From accepting deliveries to fulfilling orders, every aspect of warehouse operations is in your hands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/937d8ad4c89dfc00e698d0ff99a7246a.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Forklift Fun: Take control of the forklift and maneuver it through the warehouse environment. Upgrade your forklift to handle heavier loads and increase efficiency.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/b74881971674bec66d265fefbcf6eb7b.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Diverse Pallet Management: Deal with a variety of pallet types, each with its own storage requirements. From regular pallets to refrigerated and hazardous ones, make sure that every item is stored safely and correctly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/f058927b13d0bd020c916bc1ede85d33.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Expansion: Customize and expand your warehouse to optimize efficiency and maximize profits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.poster.avif?t=1735400495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.webm?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2907930/extras/429abbdde2cc7a5b6fddef03d1920237.mp4?t=1735400495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
